  "texts": [
    "By incorporating real-time data into GPT-Neo, we have showcased the potential for LLMs to remain current with the latest information, thereby significantly improving their utility across a wide range of applications.",
    "The contributions of this study extend beyond the immediate enhancements to GPT-Neo, offering a scalable and efficient methodology for updating LLMs without the need for comprehensive retraining.",
    "This approach reduces the resource consumption typically associated with maintaining the relevance of LLMs, presenting a viable solution to one of the most pressing issues in the field of AI.",
    "The incremental knowledge enrichment method promises to reshape the development of LLMs, paving the way for more dynamic, adaptable, and efficient models.",
    "As we continue to refine this approach and expand its application to other models, the potential impacts on both the field of AI and its myriad applications are profound."
